Interface InitializableFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Factory
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    StrategyFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultStrategyFactory

    public interface InitializableFactory
extends Factory
    An interface for an initializable Factory. All factories that are initialized by the FactoryManager must implement this interface.
